    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps produced by Tiffany Studios beginning in 1895 having shades made of various types of stained glass, sometimes set in intricate leaded patterns. Other lamps have shades resembling flowers made of iridescent glass. Lamps produced by Tiffany Studios beginning in 1895 having shades made of various types of stained glass, sometimes set in intricate leaded patterns. Other lamps have shades resembling flowers made of iridescent glass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
